HER BIG SURPRISE IS.

02:22.707 --> 02:23.708
-WISH I KNEW.

02:33.022 --> 02:36.286
IF YOU'D RATHER GO JOGGING
THAN SURF SKIING, NO PROBLEMO.

02:36.417 --> 02:39.071
-NO, THAT'S OKAY.
I WANNA SURF SKI WITH YOU, DAD.

02:39.202 --> 02:41.248
-YOU KNOW HER?
-HER NAME IS BRIDGET BOWERS.

02:41.378 --> 02:44.164
SHE'S HAVING
A PARTY THIS WEEKEND,
BUT I DIDN'T GET INVITED.

02:46.688 --> 02:48.994
-SHE'S HEADING BACK THIS WAY
IF YOU WANNA TALK TO HER.

02:49.865 --> 02:51.345
-NO, COME ON.
LET'S GET OUT OF HERE.

02:51.475 --> 02:52.824
LET'S GET GOING.
-NO, NO, NO, WHAT'S YOUR HURRY?

02:52.955 --> 02:54.435
COME ON. NO, IT'S OKAY.

02:54.565 --> 02:55.392
EXCUSE ME.

02:55.523 --> 02:57.612
UH, YOUR NAME BRIDGET?

02:58.221 --> 02:59.831
YOU KNOW MY SON HOBIE.

03:03.270 --> 03:06.838
-BUCHANNON. WE, UM...
WE HAVE SOCIAL STUDIES TOGETHER.

03:06.969 --> 03:10.015
-OH! OH, YEAH,
YOU'RE THE BOY THAT
ALWAYS HAS SAND IN HIS SHOES.

03:10.146 --> 03:12.670
-NO, WELL...
-I THINK THAT'S SO COOL.

03:14.150 --> 03:15.891
IT'S LIKE BRINGING THE BEACH
WITH YOU TO SCHOOL.

03:16.021 --> 03:18.241
-YEAH, MAYBE I GUESS I DO.

03:18.372 --> 03:20.504
-LISTEN, I'M HAVING A PARTY
FRIDAY NIGHT.

03:20.635 --> 03:22.071
YOU WANNA COME?

03:22.202 --> 03:23.551
-YEAH, SURE.

03:24.421 --> 03:27.294
-GREAT.
BRING SAND IN YOUR SHOES,
AND WE'LL MAKE IT A BEACH PARTY.

03:28.033 --> 03:29.905
SEE YOU.
-BYE.

03:31.472 --> 03:33.474
-SEE, PAL?
ALL YOU GOTTA DO IS TALK TO HER.

03:33.604 --> 03:35.258
-YEAH, ME. NOT YOU.

03:35.389 --> 03:36.868
-AW, COME ON, MAN.

03:37.521 --> 03:40.089
-HI, YOU'RE BRIDGET.
YOU KNOW MY SON HOBIE,
DON'T YOU?

03:41.177 --> 03:42.570
-GOTTA SEIZE THE MOMENT, COOKIE.

03:42.700 --> 03:44.398
-I WOULD IF YOU WOULDN'T
HAVE DONE IT FOR ME.

03:45.137 --> 03:46.226
-LET'S HIT IT.

03:49.098 --> 03:50.969
LET'S GO!

